# Non-secret, deploy-time config for the GMATWiz Functions.
# Copy to functions/.env to override. NEVER put OPENAI_API_KEY here — it is a
# Functions secret (firebase functions:secrets:set OPENAI_API_KEY).

# Default OpenAI model (per-call `model` in the request still wins).
# OPENAI_MODEL="gpt-4.1-mini"

# Enforce Firebase App Check on gmatGenerate. Leave off until the web + iOS
# clients send App Check tokens, or every call will be rejected.
# GMAT_ENFORCE_APP_CHECK="true"
